item.dc:creator: @The_Owner_CJ The Owner CJ
item.description:
@The_Owner_CJ wrote:

The problem probably is that the .java cannot understand what the statements mean, what you probably need to do is to import a file in this:
location: class server.model.players.packets.ClickItem
How to fix:
I’m guessing, but i’m pretty sure that this is what you need to add at the top with all the other imports:

Code:

import server.model.players.packets.ClickItem;
